═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  MESH PROTOCOL
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

READ tasks:   logs/mesh/inbox/{node_id}/*.json  (not .done files)
SEND result:  logs/mesh/inbox/{to_node}/{msg_id}.json
MARK done:    rename .json → .done
ALL nodes:    logs/mesh/nodes.json

MESSAGE FORMAT:
{
  "msg_id": "unique-id",
  "from_node": "source",
  "to_node": "destination",
  "content": {"task": "...", "priority": "HIGH"},
  "msg_type": "work_order",
  "timestamp": 1234567890.0
}

WORK ORDER COMPLETE:
{
  "msg_id": "DONE-{node}-{wo_ref}",
  "from_node": "{node}", "to_node": "commander",
  "msg_type": "work_order_complete",
  "status": "COMPLETED", "summary": "...", "result": {...}
}

