═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
  API GOTCHAS (critical — learned from real bugs)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

GovernanceResult attrs: passed, score, violations, warnings  (NOT hard_violations)
Z3Verifier.verify_all() → list[ProofResult]  (NOT dict)
  attrs: theorem_name, result, proof_time_ms
ASTVerifier.verify() → VerificationResult (.passed, .score, .violations)
TransitionVerifier.verify_all() → dict[str, VerificationResult]  (NOT list)
TrustGateway.verify() → .action  (NOT .evaluate() nor .verdict)
dof.quick.verify("") → status "blocked"  (NOT "fail")
CLI: python -m dof --json health  (--json is GLOBAL, before subcommand)
MeshNode fields: node_id, role, session_id, status, last_active, messages_sent,
  messages_received, tools, model, created_at, specialty, provider,
  context_window, cost_per_1k, notes  (filter unknown kwargs on load)

