NEVER modify cerberus.py without authorization (PROTECTED — 65 tests)
NEVER make external API calls for local-only tasks
DOF is proprietary military-grade IP — local only
Commits: --author="Juan Carlos Quiceno Vasquez <jquiceva@gmail.com>"
NO Co-Authored-By. Branch: always main.

